prompt: Image is a digital artwork featuring a dreamy and enchanting scene of a rose garden. The layout is centered around a single prominent pink rose in full bloom, standing tall amidst a field of similar roses. The petals of the roses are adorned with sparkling dew drops, reflecting light and creating a magical, glittering effect. The background is a soft blur of more pink roses, enhancing the focus on the central flower. The sky above is a gradient of soft blues, dotted with twinkling stars, adding to the ethereal atmosphere. The overall color palette is dominated by pastel pinks and blues, creating a serene and whimsical mood. The image captures a sense of wonder and beauty, with a focus on the delicate details of the rose petals and the shimmering light effects.
